BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2ZSI5iWBOFEeg685NExph
SUMMARY:Psychedelic Salon: Psychedelics & Grief
DTSTAMP:20260411T040854Z
DTSTART:20260507T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Grief is one of the most universal yet isolating experiences we
	 endure—and psychedelics may offer a path through it. This Salon explores 
	how substances like psilocybin\\\, MDMA\\\, and 5-MeO-DMT are being used t
	o support those navigating loss\\\, whether from death\\\, identity shifts
	\\\, or life transitions. This session sheds light on how altered states c
	an help us reconnect to love\\\, soften the sharp edges of sorrow\\\, and 
	reorient to a life forever changed. Attendees will gain insight into the s
	cience and integration practices that support emotional processing and mea
	ning-making in the context of grief.\n\nhttps://townhallseattle.org/event/
	psychedelic-salon-psychedelics-grief/\n\nFrom Town Hall Seattle
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/psychedelic-salon-psychedelics-grief/
LOCATION:The Wyncote NW Forum\\\, 1119 8th Ave (Entrance off Seneca St.)\\\
	, Seattle\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:town-hall-seattle
CATEGORIES:Town Hall Seattle
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT
END:VEVENT
